@startuml
[*] --> StartCampaign: Manager and staff are assigned
StartCampaign --> ActivateCampaign: Everything is approved and contract is signed
ActivateCampaign --> PrepareAdverts: Campaign started
PrepareAdverts --> ApproveScheduleAdverts: Adverts prepared
ApproveScheduleAdverts --> RunAdverts: Adverts scheduled
RunAdverts --> ExtendAdjustCampaign: Adverts running
ExtendAdjustCampaign --> CompleteCampaign: Campaign extended or adjusted
CompleteCampaign --> FinalStatement: All adverts finished
FinalStatement --> HandlePayment: Campaign completed
HandlePayment --> RefundAmountLessThanRequired: Amount paid is less than required
RefundAmountLessThanRequired --> MarkAsPaid: Generate refund
MarkAsPaid --> WaitForCorrectBalance: Amount paid exceeds the required amount
WaitForCorrectBalance --> SettleCorrectBalance: Wait for correct balance to be settled
SettleCorrectBalance --> MarkAsPaid: Full amount properly paid
MarkAsPaid --> ArchiveCampaign: Campaign marked as paid
ArchiveCampaign --> ReleaseStaffManagers: Campaign archived and staff released
FinalStatement --> [*]: All adverts finished
@enduml
